Christine Ayo Achen nke a makwaara dị ka Achen Christine Ayo (amụrụ na 7 Julaị, na afọ 1983) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na onye nchịkwa nke Uganda. Ọ bụ nwanyị nnọchi anya distrikti nke Alebtong na 10th parliament nke Uganda. Ọ nwere njikọ na National Resistance Movement na-achịkwa otu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị. Ọ bụkwa onye na-achọ ịbụ onye omeiwu nwanyị maka afọ 2021-2026 na Alebtong.
Christine nwere diplọma na ọmụmụ mmepe site na Nzamizi Training Institute of social development.

Ọ bụ onye omeiwu na ụlọ omeiwu nke Uganda kemgbe afọ 2016 ruo taa. Ọ na-eje ozi na ọrụ ọzọ dị ka onye otu kọmitii na Gender Labour and Social Development na PAC ime obodo gọọmentị na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke Uganda. Ọ bụ onye otu Uganda Women Parliamentary Association nke 10th Parliament of Uganda. Tupu ntuli aka nke afọ 2021, o nwere onye na-asọmpi maka oche nwanyị omebe iwu nke Alebtong District, Ms Barbra Akech.
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị omeiwu vootu ee na ọgụgụ nke abụọ nke Iwu Ndezigharị Iwu na afọ 2017.
Ọ lụrụ di. Ọ bụ onye Anglịkan site n'okwukwe.
